Description: It has many more pages than the final version. It is clear that the author made many corrections and  adjustments. In this copy the chapters have titles.
Notes:
Title written on the outside of the carpet in which the tapestry was. Numerous erasures, add-ons and handwritten corrections. Text: black ink. Corrections: pencil, blue ink, black ink. It had several handwritten sheets inserted without being numbered and without any indication regarding the place they should take in the final text (indexed separately from AS-AA1-04 to AS-AA1-21). Each chapter was stapled with a pin or with a paper clip (rusty). Page 76 cuted by half.
